 AIM回应国王演讲，呼吁新政府“保护英国独立场馆” https://www.nme.com/news/music/aim-responds-to-kings-speech-calls-on-new-government-to-protect-the-uks-independent-venues-3775868?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=旨在响应国王关于新政府保护英国独立场地的讲话呼吁Laura MolloyWed, 17 Jul 2024 18:36:06 +0000 Music NewsNewsPolitics https://www.nme.com/?p=3775868 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 7 月 17 日，国王查理三世在上议院议会开幕式上宣读国王演讲。图片来源：Kirsty Wigglesworth - WPA Pool/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该组织还对政府引入人工智能立法的计划做出了反应</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aim-responds-to-kings-speech-calls-on-new-government-to-protect-the-uks-independent-venues-3775868">《AIM》回应国王演讲，呼吁新政府“保护英国独立场馆”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 7 月 17 日，国王查理三世在上议院议会开幕式上宣读国王演讲。图片来源：Kirsty Wigglesworth - WPA Pool/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/King-Charles-III-reads-the-Kings-Speech-at-the-State-Opening-of-Parliament-in-the-House-of-Lords-on-July-17-2024.-Credit_-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.aim.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">独立音乐协会（AIM）</a>对今天的国王演讲做出了回应，敦促政府保护独立场所并确保英国音乐的多元化未来。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-industry-responds-to-lisa-nandy-mp-being-named-secretary-of-state-for-culture-media-and-sport-3772606">音乐界对 Lisa Nandy MP 被任命为文化、媒体和体育国务秘书做出回应</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天早些时候（7 月 17 日），查尔斯国王在上议院发表了工党政府的首次国王演讲。讲话阐述了政府未来几个月的优先事项，以及他们希望在该党大选获胜后在下届议会会议上通过的法案。</p><p>除了列出的 39 项法案之外，还包括加强地方经济、改革学徒税以及对人工智能 (AI) 开发者提出更严格要求的计划。</p><p> AIM 临时首席执行官 Gee Davy 现已对演讲作出回应，敦促新政府“在住房和规划目标中加强‘变革推动者原则’，以保护英国的独立场馆和建筑中的音乐感觉就像一个家。”</p><p>这是在现场音乐领域的一段时期的斗争中，音乐场所Trust的2023年报告显示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">目前的场所目前以每周两次的速度关闭</a>。仅去年，仅去年就关闭了125个基层场所 - 造成4,000个工作岗位，不再可能发生14,500个活动，而音乐家失去了193,230个机会。</p><p>音乐行业演讲的另一个关键时刻是新政府通过引入立法来加强当地经济的计划，以赋予都会市长和联合当局的新权力。戴维说：“这将有助于确保音乐在英国的每个地区和国家都能蓬勃发展。” </p><figure id="attachment_3577631" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3577631" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3577631" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Night-And-Day-@2000x1270.jpg" alt="公主去2021年11月29日在英格兰曼彻斯特的夜间和白天的蝴蝶博物馆演出。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Night-And-Day-@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Night-And-Day-@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Night-And-Day-@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Night-And-Day-@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Night-And-Day-@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Night-And-Day-@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3577631" class="wp-caption-text">公主去2021年11月29日在英格兰曼彻斯特的夜间和白天的蝴蝶博物馆演出。图片来源：Shirlaine Forrest/Wireimage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>演讲还强调了政府针对人工智能（AI）提出立法的计划。 4月，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-smith">Robert Smith</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">Stevie Wonder</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a>在内的一群艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-robert-smith-more-sign-open-letter-against-predatory-use-of-ai-in-music-3612507">在音乐中签署了一封公开的信警告</a>。</p><p>通过这封信，非营利组织的艺术家权利联盟要求开发人员，技术公司以及平台和数字音乐服务“承诺他们不会开发或部署AI音乐生成技术，内容或破坏或取代人类的工具词曲作者和艺术家的艺术性，或否认我们为我们的作品提供公平的赔偿。”</p><p>这封信继续说：“未经检查，AI将开始进行一场竞赛，从而降低我们的工作价值，并阻止我们得到相当补偿。对人类创造力的这种攻击必须停止。我们必须防止AI捕食专业艺术家的声音和相似之处，侵犯创作者的权利并破坏音乐生态系统。”</p><p>在演讲中，查尔斯国王说，新政府将“寻求制定适当的立法，以对旨在开发最强大人工智能模型的人们提出要求。”</p><p> AIM对此表示欢迎，戴维（Davy）说：“ Aim为寻找AI的负责任框架的建议表示赞赏。”</p><p> AIM还欢迎计划扩大学徒征税的改革，称他们希望这将“使各种规模的企业能够参与并为年轻人提供机会；并希望工人增加的支持将包括自由职业者。”</p><p>戴维接着说，目标是“期待在新议会期间与政府紧密合作，为独立音乐创造最支持的环境，长期以来，在全球进步和促进英国文化中长期以来发挥了至关重要的作用。”</p><p>他继续说：“这对于伟大的英国音乐来说，这对于辉煌而多样的未来至关重要。”</p><p>本月初， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-industry-responds-to-lisa-nandy-mp-being-named-secretary-of-state-for-culture-media-and-sport-3772606">音乐行业对丽莎·南迪国会议员任命为文化，媒体和体育的国务卿的消息做出了反应</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3772608" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3772608" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3772608" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lisa-nandy-MP-2024.jpg" alt="丽莎·南迪" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lisa-nandy-MP-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lisa-nandy-MP-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lisa-nandy-MP-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lisa-nandy-MP-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lisa-nandy-MP-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lisa-nandy-MP-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3772608" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024年7月6日在唐宁街举行的第一次内阁会议之后，文化，媒体和体育部长丽莎·南迪（Lisa Nandy）留下了第10名。</figcaption></figure><p>戴维对任命做出了回应，他说：“借助丽莎·南迪（Lisa Nandy）在升级和国际发展方面的经验，我们希望她将帮助取得成功的成功，并为英国各个地区和国家的各种独立音乐社区取得成功，并为维持英国独立独立的出口支持提供了强有力的出口支持音乐的全球地位。”</p><p> Nandy <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-annual-report-government-action-arena-investment-frank-turner-talent-pipeline-3389434">此前曾表示支持苦苦挣扎的夜总会和现场音乐表演场所</a>，尤其是她的选区的音乐遗产。</p><p>她在2022年告诉<em>《时报》广播电台</em>：“每个城镇都失去了他们非常强烈的夜总会，这是我们历史和遗产的一部分，在威根我们拥有北方的灵魂，我们非常想念所有这些。”</p><p> “从韦根（Wigan）来维持像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-verve">Verve</a>这样的乐队的现场音乐场所，他们可以在Wigan周围演出并演奏，现在只需要前往曼彻斯特（Manchester）才能做到这一点，这些事情在过去几十年中已经消失了。”</p><p>在大选之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/political-parties-urged-to-seize-the-moment-as-music-venue-trust-share-manifesto-for-the-grassroots-ahead-of-election-3764389">音乐场所信托基金会呼吁各方的政客“抓住这一时刻”，并帮助支持现场音乐领域</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aim-responds-to-kings-speech-calls-on-new-government-to-protect-the-uks-independent-venues-3775868">Aim Aim对King的讲话做出了回应，呼吁新政府“保护英国的独立场所”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
